request.description:
Get all publishers

returns 200 if found.

~~~~~~~~
{
  "data": {
    "publishers": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "name": "Street And Smith"
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "name": "Popular Publications"
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "name": "Warner Paperback Library"
      }
    ]
  }
}
~~~~~~~~

or 404 if not found

