request.description:
Get a specific publisher based on the publisher id in the URL e.g. `publishers/1` would get publisher with id 1

returns `200` and publisher data

~~~~~~~~
{
  "data": {
    "publishers": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "name": "Street And Smith"
      }
    ]
  }
}
~~~~~~~~

or `404` if not found

